    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/2b77ba2675354da3281f52b836895c04.avif?t=1644512139\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br>You have been summoned to an unknown castle.<br>And you will receive one mission. <br>Gather various voice data and approach the truth.<br>And you have to delete the root node of the network metabus that is connected to all that truth.<br>In that &quot;Dungeon Castle&quot; where you are.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/3f3ef3c2e69fb615688c5959a76e5fa3.poster.avif?t=1644512139\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/3f3ef3c2e69fb615688c5959a76e5fa3.webm?t=1644512139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/3f3ef3c2e69fb615688c5959a76e5fa3.mp4?t=1644512139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>&quot;You have to get through the Dungeon Castle with a torch and a weapon&quot;</strong><br>Where you are hidden in the dark, light up your way with torches, and defeat enemies who threaten you with weapons and move forward.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Action &amp; battle.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/6a12d67292a443c89ef1fb20a8442caf.poster.avif?t=1644512139\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/6a12d67292a443c89ef1fb20a8442caf.webm?t=1644512139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/6a12d67292a443c89ef1fb20a8442caf.mp4?t=1644512139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>&quot;The enemies you will meet are powerful&quot;</strong><br>If you are attacked, you will be in a very dangerous state.<br>Also, enemies can ignore your attack.<br>That's why always aim behind your enemies.<br>And try to avoid enemy attacks as much as possible.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Growth</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/6733e10a7bf99e9023518109609c84f4.poster.avif?t=1644512139\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/6733e10a7bf99e9023518109609c84f4.webm?t=1644512139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/6733e10a7bf99e9023518109609c84f4.mp4?t=1644512139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>&quot;The torches, weapons, and abilities given to you can be stronger&quot;</strong><br>Various weapons, attributes, and new abilities are essential for you to get through the dungeon.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Another dungeon</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/c6cb0630bca30685767866f92953232e.avif?t=1644512139\" width=720 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/8ac19541a9cf69c4bd5e900af74b1707.avif?t=1644512139\" width=720 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884140/extras/5f4bc923eefcf23f2fc9444b748058bd.avif?t=1644512139\" width=720 height=360 /></span><br><strong>&quot;There are other dungeons in the Dungeon Castle&quot;</strong><br>You have to clear different dungeons to get a variety of voice data. <br>Don't hesitate to try.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics of games</h2><br>- The fun of exploring and exploring dark castles.<br>- A strong sense of hitting and exhilarating combat action stand out.<br>- Nine weapons, 20 combat animations, and various abilities.<br>- Interesting main story and sub story.",
